Enterprise-grade security

Wix security experts provide threat monitoring, prevention and response in real-time, 24/7. Data at rest is protected by the strongest commercially available encryption. Plus, with proprietary machine learning, anti-DDoS, PCI DSS Level 1, Soc 2 Type 2 and much more—you’re safe on Wix.

Discover Security on Wix

Non-stop performance

Don’t worry about performance. With multi-cloud hosting, on-demand scalability and a global network of 200+ CDN nodes, your sites are set for success.
